            . I am a <rs id="t18280410-104-viclabel575" type="occupation">potatoe-merchant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-104-victim698 t18280410-104-viclabel575"></join>, and live in Well-street, Oxford-street. The prisoner came into my service on the 24th of September last, and was put into a shop of mine in Fitzroy-market - he was to account every night, when he shut up, for what he took in the day. On the 3d of November he was taken up on another charge - he never accounted to me for 9l. 15s. received from James Pritchard.</p>
